<p><i><b>Sins of a Solar Empire</b></i> is a <a href="/wiki/Science_fiction" title="Science fiction">science fiction</a> <a href="/wiki/Real-time_strategy" title="Real-time strategy">real-time strategy</a> <a href="/wiki/Video_game" title="Video game">computer game</a> developed by <a href="/wiki/Ironclad_Games" title="Ironclad Games">Ironclad Games</a> and published by <a href="/wiki/Stardock" title="Stardock">Stardock Entertainment</a> in February 2008. <i>Sins</i> is a <a href="/wiki/Real-time_strategy" title="Real-time strategy">real-time strategy</a> (RTS) game that incorporates some elements from <a href="/wiki/4X_game" title="4X game" class="mw-redirect">4X strategy games</a>; promotional materials describe it as "RT4X."<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1" title=""><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
